#define ANIMESH_STRENGTH 20000
#define WrestleWin ["A triviality. I expected a challenge, but you are merely a stain on my path, %s.","Was that supposed to be an attempt at resistance, %s? How utterly disappointing.","You are an inefficient use of my time, %s. Go, before I lose my patience.","I didn't even have to break a sweat to dismantle your pathetic efforts, %s.","The future has no room for the weak, %s. You've just proven you belong in the past.","Your efforts were as hollow as your ideology. You never stood a chance, %s.","Do you see now, %s? My intellect and power are far beyond your comprehension.","It is almost sad to watch you struggle so pointlessly, %s. Learn your place.","You have the ambition of a conqueror, %s, but the strength of a common insect.","Stop squirming, %s. Accepting your inferiority is the first step toward order.","Lesson learned, I assume? Though I doubt you possess the intellect to grasp it, %s.","You managed to last longer than the others, %s. A minor achievement in a sea of failures.","Power requires vision, %s. You lack both. That is why you fell today.","Do not be discouraged, %s. It takes a special kind of failure to lose to me.","Your resistance was annoying, %s. Now, it is finished.","You fought with spirit, %s, but spirit is no substitute for true power and command.","A respectable effort, %s, but you are still just an obstacle to be cleared.","I am the architect of the new world, %s. You are merely debris in its foundation.","You have talent, %s. Pity that it is being wasted on such a lost cause.","The dust settles, and I am still standing. The outcome was never in doubt, %s.","A valiant effort, but ultimately futile. The Green Skull does not suffer insurrection, %s.","You are more capable than most, %s. It makes your defeat all the more satisfying.","I felt your strength, %s. It was almost... adequate. Almost.","You pushed me to utilize more of my resources, %s. You should feel honored.","Even with your potential, you are nowhere near my level of strategic mastery, %s.","You almost made me use my full potential. Almost. Know your place now, %s.","A difficult struggle, but in the end, only the strong remain, %s.","Your power is commendable, %s, yet you still lack the discipline to rule.","That was almost a challenge, %s. Let's see if you can provide more next time.","The field is clear, and I remain the victor. You were a good test, %s.","Finally, a victory that leaves a lasting impression. You were a worthy test, %s.","To overcome a foe of your stature... yes, this is what victory should feel like, %s.","You have earned my temporary respect, %s. Do not mistake that for mercy.","Even the strongest must bend to the will of the Green Skull. You are no exception, %s.","This battle will be recorded in my archives as a highlight, %s. A truly superior effort."]
#define WrestleDefeat ["A fluke! Do not think this means you have won, %s! I will return!","This is impossible! My Gamma augmentation should have guaranteed dominance, %s!","You got lucky, %s. Don't let this minor setback cloud your judgment of my power.","My circuits... my concentration... this wasn't a fair fight, %s!","I am forced to retreat, %s. But know that you have made a very powerful enemy today.","Impossible... I am the future! How could someone as insignificant as you prevail, %s?","You have disrupted my calculations, %s. This isn't how the history books will read.","This cannot be happening! I, the Green Skull, will not be humiliated by a weakling, %s!","You have stolen a victory from the wrong person, %s. I will remember this.","My defeat is merely a strategic error. You have not won, you have simply delayed me, %s.","You caught me off guard, nothing more. Victory against me is a temporary illusion, %s.","I am retreating to recalibrate, %s. You have only bought yourself a moment of safety.","The tide of battle is fickle, %s. Don't get comfortable with this result.","You have utilized a strategy I didn't account for, %s. I will not make that mistake twice.","My systems are damaged, %s. You have achieved a hollow victory.","This is not over. I will analyze your tactics and ensure your next failure is absolute, %s.","You are merely an anomaly, %s. An anomaly that I will correct in due time.","Do not celebrate, %s. My resources are vast, and I will be back with more.","Today you hold the ground, %s. Tomorrow, the world will remember the Green Skull.","Your victory is a temporary disturbance in my grand design, %s.","You have power, I grant you that. But you lack the vision to rule, %s.","So, this is the strength you hide, %s? Impressive, but it won't save you for long.","I leave the field today, %s. Do not think it was because I lacked the capacity to win.","You have proven yourself a nuisance, %s. I intend to eliminate that nuisance permanently.","I will return with a strategy tailored specifically for your weaknesses, %s.","This defeat is a strategic necessity. I will retreat, but mark my words, %s, the world will still be mine.","You have fought well, %s. It is a pity you are on the wrong side of history.","I have sustained critical damage, %s. You have won this round, but the war is far from over.","You are a formidable variable, %s. I shall incorporate you into my next simulation.","Victory today, defeat tomorrow. We shall see how long your strength lasts, %s.","Unbelievable. To be bested... you have proven to be a dangerous variable, %s. We shall meet again.","You are the first to truly force my withdrawal in ages, %s. I am... intrigued.","My strategic processors are overloaded. You are indeed a peer in power, %s.","I concede this battle, %s. You have earned the right to stand against me.","A pyrrhic victory for you, %s. I will be back, and next time, I will not be so gracious."]
